plot: While Khloe anticipates her move, she realizes that she has been burglarized. Bruce encourages Brody for a golf tournament. Kourtney, Kim and Khloe head to the Big Apple to do a surprise DASH drop-by.

Khloe gets candid like never before on her divorce from Lamar. Hear how she's dealing with a broken heart and why her new habits have her family worried! Then, while packing she notices over $250,000 of Lamar's jewelry has gone missing! Can she track down the thief? Then, Bruce and Brody play in a father-son golf tournament--so will working together bring them closer or not? Finally, the girls head to New York City to find a fresh new location for their SoHo Dash shop.—Anonymous
